  <brief_title>Biomarkers and Cardiac CT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biomarkers and Cardiac Computed Tomography: Relationship Between Cardiovascular Biomarkers and Coronary Artery Disease in Patients Undergoing Cardiac Computed Tomography</official_title>
